'From Squeak3.8gamma of ''24 November 2004'' [latest update: #6639] on 7 April 2005 at 3:52:16 pm'!"Change Set:		autoLoadUpdatesDate:			7 April 2005Author:			Michael RuegerAdds the preference updateFromServerAtStartup and modifies release builder to set it to true on a release image. Default value is false though."!!ReleaseBuilderDeveloper methodsFor: 'utilities' stamp: 'mir 4/7/2005 11:56'!installPreferences	super installPreferences.	#(		(updateFromServerAtStartup true)	) do:[:spec|		Preferences setPreference: spec first toValue: spec last]! !"Postscript:"	Preferences		addPreference: #updateFromServerAtStartup		categories: #(#updates)		default: false		balloonHelp: 'If true the system will check for and load any available updates'!